snippet.textDisplay: Slow-poison: First of all, Congrats to all of us in India! Finally!! being a Bengali, I am enjoying Coke Studio Bangla too, and this song is making me go crazy... Take a bow OAFF x Savera! secondly, the depth of the lyrics actually goes along with the core of the folk song - an amazing blend, new, fresh and soo soothing to identify and differentiate a nation like India... lastly, we started with a bang - hope to meet Coke studio's uniqueness sooner than expected... A R Rahman's Coke studio is the bar - and none can touch that level yet!
snippet.textOriginal: Slow-poison: First of all, Congrats to all of us in India! Finally!! being a Bengali, I am enjoying Coke Studio Bangla too, and this song is making me go crazy...
